I'll have him replace them
with new ones.

00:22:55.292 --> 00:22:56.571
He'll be back soon.

00:23:07.875 --> 00:23:08.516
Ms. Lu.

00:23:08.867 --> 00:23:09.748
Miss Nie, you're back.

00:23:09.748 --> 00:23:10.308
Come on in.

00:23:11.988 --> 00:23:12.748
Hello.

00:23:13.228 --> 00:23:13.728
Hello.

00:23:15.827 --> 00:23:16.468
Ms. Lu,

00:23:16.788 --> 00:23:18.308
they're Yan Tuo's uncle and cousin.

00:23:18.427 --> 00:23:20.268
They'll stay with us for a while.

00:23:21.387 --> 00:23:23.028
Lin Ling and Mr. Changxi,

00:23:23.187 --> 00:23:24.948
tell Ms. Lu anything you need.

00:23:25.028 --> 00:23:26.163
Make yourselves at home.

00:23:28.827 --> 00:23:29.667
You are?

00:23:30.187 --> 00:23:31.308
Liu Changxi.

00:23:32.347 --> 00:23:34.387
Did you enjoy the dumplings last time?

00:23:35.748 --> 00:23:37.107
So it really was you.

00:23:39.548 --> 00:23:40.107
Okay.

00:23:41.587 --> 00:23:42.387
Hello, Ms. Lu.

00:23:42.548 --> 00:23:43.708
Just call me Lin Ling.

00:23:44.508 --> 00:23:45.667
Hello, Miss Lin Ling.

00:23:47.508 --> 00:23:49.708
Your father's dumplings
were very delicious.

00:23:50.147 --> 00:23:51.587
Those dumplings last time

00:23:51.867 --> 00:23:52.948
didn't last long with me.

00:23:52.948 --> 00:23:53.988
You misunderstood.

00:23:54.667 --> 00:23:55.988
I'm an old bachelor.

00:23:56.187 --> 00:23:57.748
I don't have such a pretty daughter.

00:23:58.788 --> 00:23:59.667
I misunderstood.

00:23:59.667 --> 00:24:00.167
Yes.

00:24:00.708 --> 00:24:01.627
It's fine, Ms. Lu.

00:24:01.748 --> 00:24:03.308
You'll get to know each other later.

00:24:03.468 --> 00:24:04.708
Show them the guest rooms.

00:24:04.948 --> 00:24:06.427
I'll be away for a few days.

00:24:06.627 --> 00:24:07.948
Take good care of them.

00:24:08.347 --> 00:24:09.468
Okay, don't worry.

00:24:09.788 --> 00:24:10.427
Give me that.

00:24:10.427 --> 00:24:11.268
I can do it.

00:24:11.268 --> 00:24:11.867
Let's go.

00:24:12.068 --> 00:24:13.187
This way, please.

00:24:14.147 --> 00:24:14.867
Mr. Changxi.

00:24:39.708 --> 00:24:41.107
Nuwa holds the compass.

00:24:41.308 --> 00:24:42.587
Fuxi grasps the square.

00:24:43.508 --> 00:24:44.708
Without rules,

00:24:45.387 --> 00:24:46.627
there's no order.

00:25:02.627 --> 00:25:03.827
Being Mad Blade

00:25:04.627 --> 00:25:06.347
in secret for all these years,

00:25:06.547 --> 00:25:08.186
was revealing yourself to an outsider

00:25:08.706 --> 00:25:09.307
truly worth it?

00:25:13.186 --> 00:25:14.466
It wasn't just for him.

00:25:14.907 --> 00:25:15.986
It was also for Jiang.

00:25:16.706 --> 00:25:17.426
Besides,

00:25:18.387 --> 00:25:19.466
Yan Tuo is not an outsider.

00:25:20.355 --> 00:25:20.996
Alright.

00:25:21.355 --> 00:25:22.196
Alright.

00:25:23.196 --> 00:25:24.956
Then let me tell you a story.

00:25:26.315 --> 00:25:28.395
Remember when we couldn't figure it out?

00:25:28.756 --> 00:25:29.835
Since Li Ergou

00:25:29.835 --> 00:25:31.835
was Lin Xirou's first blood bag,

00:25:32.676 --> 00:25:34.756
how did Lin Ling come about?

00:25:35.716 --> 00:25:38.036
Xing Shen
had her background investigated.

00:25:38.516 --> 00:25:41.595
Li Ergou, who disappeared
from Roadsound Mining back then...

00:25:42.155 --> 00:25:43.835
He was actually Lin Ling's close kin.

00:25:51.916 --> 00:25:53.476
Lin Ling and I saw Li Ergou's photo

00:25:53.476 --> 00:25:54.956
at Mr. Changxi's place.

00:25:56.276 --> 00:25:58.555
I thought Lin Ling
acted strangely back then.

00:25:59.595 --> 00:26:00.476
It felt like

00:26:01.875 --> 00:26:03.996
she could sense something.

00:26:07.956 --> 00:26:10.196
When Lin Xirou first gained footing,

00:26:10.196 --> 00:26:11.956
she tracked down Li Ergou's parents.

00:26:12.875 --> 00:26:14.155
She offered them a fortune

00:26:15.075 --> 00:26:16.516
to have another child.

00:26:17.595 --> 00:26:20.315
She said regardless
of gender or quantity,

00:26:20.795 --> 00:26:21.875
if they had more children,

00:26:22.155 --> 00:26:23.196
she'd take them all.

00:26:24.555 --> 00:26:26.555
Li Ergou's parents had already divorced,

00:26:26.555 --> 00:26:28.516
but moved back together for the money.

00:26:35.436 --> 00:26:36.916
So Li Ergou was actually

00:26:37.196 --> 00:26:38.436
Lin Ling's brother.

00:26:39.635 --> 00:26:42.036
So, to maintain her blood bag supply,

00:26:42.355 --> 00:26:44.875
Lin Xirou paid Li Ergou's parents
to keep having children.

00:26:45.716 --> 00:26:47.075
How many more did they have?

00:26:47.315 --> 00:26:48.276
Just Lin Ling.

00:26:48.996 --> 00:26:50.555
Later, they fought over the money

00:26:50.956 --> 00:26:52.875
and died together in a car crash.

00:26:56.875 --> 00:26:58.595
Lin Ling's existence in this world

00:26:59.115 --> 00:27:00.196
was just a transaction,

00:27:01.795 --> 00:27:04.436
a tool purchased by Lin Xirou

00:27:05.516 --> 00:27:06.676
to breed more blood bags.

00:27:07.795 --> 00:27:08.956
Out of a family of four,

00:27:09.555 --> 00:27:11.115
only a tool survived.

00:27:12.355 --> 00:27:13.795
Not sure whether to feel relieved

00:27:14.716 --> 00:27:15.676
or sorrowful about it.

00:27:17.676 --> 00:27:18.676
Yan Tuo once said

00:27:19.355 --> 00:27:20.395
those kept in the dark

00:27:20.756 --> 00:27:21.956
live more carefree lives.

00:27:23.516 --> 00:27:24.395
Let these matters

00:27:24.756 --> 00:27:26.075
stay buried within us.

00:28:10.555 --> 00:28:12.635
Big Head

00:28:13.315 --> 00:28:15.155
got guarding down.

00:28:15.155 --> 00:28:15.916
Shut up.

00:28:16.476 --> 00:28:18.155
Others have guard dogs,

00:28:18.395 --> 00:28:19.916
and I have Big Head.

00:28:20.155 --> 00:28:21.155
Enough already.

00:28:21.155 --> 00:28:22.875
I said shut up.

00:28:26.555 --> 00:28:27.115
My beard.

00:28:37.516 --> 00:28:38.555
We've received reports

00:28:39.355 --> 00:28:41.436
of suspicious activity
near this location.

00:28:41.916 --> 00:28:42.996
We'll inspect the area.

00:28:45.355 --> 00:28:46.716
The mine's long been abandoned.

00:28:46.956 --> 00:28:48.355
There's no suspicious activity.

00:28:48.756 --> 00:28:50.236
Look at us.

00:28:50.236 --> 00:28:51.395
Do we look suspicious?

00:28:51.395 --> 00:28:52.115
Actually, yes.

00:28:52.355 --> 00:28:53.795
Why hang around an abandoned mine?

00:28:54.115 --> 00:28:54.996
Illegal mining?

00:28:55.595 --> 00:28:57.436
Illegal mining's a criminal offense.

00:28:57.436 --> 00:28:58.276
We'd never do that.

00:28:58.676 --> 00:28:59.355
We're here

00:28:59.355 --> 00:29:00.635
just because the boss sent us

00:29:00.635 --> 00:29:01.795
to watch the equipment.

00:29:02.115 --> 00:29:03.476
There are zero workers here.

00:29:03.756 --> 00:29:04.835
What could we possibly dig?

00:29:04.996 --> 00:29:06.236
No one at all?

00:29:07.196 --> 00:29:07.996
No.

00:29:10.996 --> 00:29:11.795
Show us.

00:29:11.795 --> 00:29:12.555
Wait a second.

00:29:13.355 --> 00:29:14.036
Gentlemen,

00:29:14.756 --> 00:29:16.716
there's no problem with looking around,

00:29:17.115 --> 00:29:20.756
but which department are you from?

00:29:21.476 --> 00:29:23.555
Please show your IDs if possible,

00:29:24.075 --> 00:29:25.476
so I can report to my boss.

00:29:25.476 --> 00:29:26.036
Right?

00:29:35.555 --> 00:29:38.315
Xicang Mining Safety Administration,
Liu Zhengming?

00:29:57.635 --> 00:29:58.555
The area is clear.

00:29:59.476 --> 00:30:00.036
Coming.

00:30:07.379 --> 00:30:10.803
(613, Youtang County)

00:30:29.795 --> 00:30:30.756
This place is huge.

00:30:30.835 --> 00:30:31.956
Let's split up.

00:30:32.996 --> 00:30:34.996
Okay, keep in touch.

00:30:34.996 --> 00:30:35.956
- Got it.
- Got it.

00:30:46.995 --> 00:30:48.947
(Helmet Required in Mining Area)

00:31:58.963 --> 00:32:02.451
(Turn of the Century, Yan Family)

00:32:09.219 --> 00:32:09.858
Any findings?

00:32:10.579 --> 00:32:12.378
(Roadsound Mining)
No obvious leads left.

00:32:12.898 --> 00:32:13.779
We can enter the mine.

00:32:17.827 --> 00:32:18.827
The keyhole's clean.

00:32:19.106 --> 00:32:20.387
Regular access likely.

00:32:22.827 --> 00:32:23.907
They talked.

00:32:23.907 --> 00:32:25.546
Lin Xirou and her followers

00:32:25.546 --> 00:32:26.546
come regularly.

00:32:26.546 --> 00:32:27.106
Copy that.

00:32:28.546 --> 00:32:29.706
I'll go down with Yu Rong.

00:32:30.186 --> 00:32:31.467
You and Big Head wait outside.

00:32:31.555 --> 00:32:32.356
Can you do that?

00:32:32.436 --> 00:32:32.936
Perhaps...

00:32:39.996 --> 00:32:42.075
We just found these
in the security department.

00:32:59.971 --> 00:33:00.971
(Security Department)
Which one is it?

00:33:02.252 --> 00:33:04.172
The one
with the girl group profile picture.

00:33:04.172 --> 00:33:06.772
(Xiong Black)

00:33:06.772 --> 00:33:09.732
Xiong Bu... Bu Lai Ke?

00:33:10.371 --> 00:33:12.252
Black. It's English.

00:33:12.652 --> 00:33:13.252
What's that?

00:33:14.531 --> 00:33:16.332
The English word for 'Hei.'

00:33:16.772 --> 00:33:17.451
Hei?

00:33:18.692 --> 00:33:19.812
So, it's Xiong Hei?

00:33:19.971 --> 00:33:20.851
Right.

00:33:21.155 --> 00:33:22.195
Xiong Black.

00:33:22.874 --> 00:33:24.035
That's quite fancy.

00:33:42.314 --> 00:33:42.954
Ms. Lin,

00:33:43.354 --> 00:33:44.874
these are new blood bags for You Peng.

00:33:44.995 --> 00:33:45.794
Please pick one.

00:33:47.354 --> 00:33:48.394
They're all healthy

00:33:48.754 --> 00:33:50.075
with simple social connections.

00:33:51.155 --> 00:33:52.954
If they go missing,
no one will look for them.

00:33:54.834 --> 00:33:56.155
How about the mine?

00:33:56.754 --> 00:33:58.578
Just got an update. All is well.

00:33:58.578 --> 00:33:59.986
(Personnel Reserve, Zhou Bingyu)

00:34:01.874 --> 00:34:04.594
(Sun Minjie, Wang Yuehai)

00:34:06.322 --> 00:34:07.602
(Sun Minjie)
Let's go with this one.

00:34:08.075 --> 00:34:09.314
You Peng has a large build.

00:34:09.715 --> 00:34:11.035
Let's pick a big guy for him.

00:34:11.914 --> 00:34:12.715
Right on it.

00:34:13.394 --> 00:34:14.794
When You Peng is transformed,

00:34:14.794 --> 00:34:16.195
he will definitely be useful.

00:34:16.834 --> 00:34:17.555
Go do your work.

00:34:17.595 --> 00:34:18.155
Okay.

00:35:07.139 --> 00:35:09.460
If this place
is really Lin Xirou's lair,

00:35:09.980 --> 00:35:11.139
what's below

00:35:11.699 --> 00:35:12.860
is hard to say.

00:35:14.699 --> 00:35:16.099
If you're not ready yet,

00:35:16.460 --> 00:35:17.300
I can go down alone.

00:36:59.939 --> 00:37:00.771
Luo.

00:37:02.019 --> 00:37:03.075
Luo.

