♪The shapeless fire
clings to matter to illuminate♪

00:37:18.603 --> 00:37:22.923
♪Yet malice in darkness
defies the flame's pursuit♪

00:37:22.923 --> 00:37:27.363
♪A noble name must do righteous deeds♪

00:37:27.363 --> 00:37:29.803
♪After sunrise,
even wise words falter in truth♪

00:37:29.803 --> 00:37:33.883
♪Heaven-forged fire
scorches flesh and bone♪

00:37:33.883 --> 00:37:38.243
♪Dig out the truth buried
beneath the earth♪

00:37:38.243 --> 00:37:41.539
♪Heaven-sent tides can't
quench this reckless fire♪

00:37:41.539 --> 00:37:46.275
(Closed)

00:37:46.275 --> 00:37:50.851
(Changxi Dumplings,
Joy Overflows with Blessings)

00:37:51.323 --> 00:37:55.603
♪Truth's madness is hiding
under the surface♪

00:37:55.603 --> 00:38:00.163
♪The large waves are rolling
towards the sky♪

00:38:00.163 --> 00:38:07.883
♪Farewell to the old times,
and scenes fade away one by one♪